name: Harden Up Shirt
description:
Custom hand screen printed harden up shirt with eco friendly white ink. This design also includes the American flag on the sleeve and the painted revolver down the front of the shirt.


The perfect 50/50 blend creates a soft and comfortable slim-fitting T-shirt.  Unlike other Poly-Cotton t-shirts on the market, American Apparel is made with combed cotton, giving it an ultra soft, worn in feel and superior drape. This shirt is breathable allowing you to move freely without feeling stuck in a shirt! 



Poly-Cotton (50% Polyester / 50% Combed-Cotton) construction
Durable rib neckband
Fits as a slim comfortable tshirt
Fabric weight 3.7 oz/yd² (125 g/m²)

 **This style shirt is UNISEX, both women and men can wear this style, so feel free to order for anyone!**


Male model is wearing a size M 


**Please note when choosing colors, in clothing, heather refers to interwoven yarns of mixed colors producing flecks of an alternate color. It is typically used to mix multiple shades of grey or grey with another color to produce a muted shade.

 

We are able to print our harden up shirt on any color shirt at no extra cost to you. Please select the color shirt and size you would like and place in your cart. 

 

*****Please note color of your custom Ink in "notes to seller" at checkout, if blank, WHITE (as shown) will be printed***** 
*INK also available in Red, Pink, Dk Blue, Lt Blue, White, Gray. 
-Please allow 10 business days to ship out custom color requests.-
